1
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:50,448
=Gorgeous Dream=

2
00:00:50,472 --> 00:00:52,180
(Adapted from the novel
"The Charming Evil Consort")

3
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:55,020
=Episode 11=

4
00:00:59,252 --> 00:01:01,493
Madam Liu, you have a cold constitution.

5
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:04,290
A few doses should help
warm your body up.

6
00:01:04,550 --> 00:01:06,470
It won't affect
your chances of having children.

7
00:01:07,613 --> 00:01:08,292
Thank you.

8
00:01:27,372 --> 00:01:28,693
Master Liu, your pulse…

9
00:01:30,773 --> 00:01:31,812
Be frank.

10
00:01:36,012 --> 00:01:38,790
It's a condition of innate weakness
in the vital essence of the kidneys.

11
00:01:38,812 --> 00:01:39,493
You may

12
00:01:40,773 --> 00:01:42,413
never have children in this lifetime.

13
00:01:43,053 --> 00:01:44,133
Nonsense!

14
00:01:46,253 --> 00:01:47,693
I already have a son.

15
00:01:50,053 --> 00:01:50,890
Please calm yourself.

16
00:01:51,572 --> 00:01:53,452
A pulse doesn't lie.

17
00:01:53,973 --> 00:01:56,053
If you once had a child,

18
00:01:56,452 --> 00:01:57,092
then…

19
00:01:58,173 --> 00:02:00,173
it must have been a stroke of chance.

20
00:02:02,253 --> 00:02:02,973
What did you say?

21
00:02:03,812 --> 00:02:04,773
Say it again.

22
00:02:06,812 --> 00:02:09,013
I wouldn't dare speak carelessly.

23
00:02:12,070 --> 00:02:13,400
They call this the "Wilted Glory."

24
00:02:13,412 --> 00:02:14,310
Take it for seven days,

25
00:02:14,733 --> 00:02:16,013
and even a healthy young man

26
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,890
will have a pulse
as weak as rotting wood.

27
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:19,790
Not even the most
highly skilled physician

28
00:02:19,972 --> 00:02:21,573
can detect otherwise.

29
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:39,412
(Steadfast Loyalty)

30
00:03:02,062 --> 00:03:04,462
(Memorial tablet of Liu Wenyu)

31
00:03:17,573 --> 00:03:18,412
Smash it all!

32
00:03:22,262 --> 00:03:23,875
(Memorial tablet of Liu Wenyu)

33
00:03:26,453 --> 00:03:27,293
What are you doing?

34
00:03:31,212 --> 00:03:32,733
What do you think you're doing?

35
00:03:33,053 --> 00:03:33,773
Stop!

36
00:03:45,173 --> 00:03:45,812
Stay back!

37
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:46,990
Go away! Get away from me!

38
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:47,853
Don't come any closer!

39
00:03:48,013 --> 00:03:48,520
Get down from there!

40
00:03:48,532 --> 00:03:49,493
Liu Qinghe!

41
00:03:49,690 --> 00:03:50,773
What are you trying to do?

42
00:03:51,573 --> 00:03:53,132
Pull her down!

43
00:04:00,972 --> 00:04:01,532
Burn it!

44
00:04:15,572 --> 00:04:16,812
No!

45
00:04:26,493 --> 00:04:27,533
Liu Qinghe!

46
00:04:28,012 --> 00:04:29,213
Liu Qinghe!

47
00:04:30,093 --> 00:04:31,772
Liu Qinghe!

48
00:04:33,012 --> 00:04:35,533
He's your own flesh and blood!

49
00:04:36,772 --> 00:04:39,812
Why are you doing this?

50
00:04:40,012 --> 00:04:41,550
- Why?
- An illegitimate child doesn't deserve

51
00:04:41,932 --> 00:04:44,213
a place in the Liu ancestral tomb.

52
00:04:46,372 --> 00:04:47,413
You wretch.

53
00:04:48,173 --> 00:04:50,372
How dare you taint the Liu bloodline

54
00:04:50,733 --> 00:04:52,533
and disgrace the entire clan!

55
00:04:53,932 --> 00:04:54,932
An illegitimate child

56
00:04:55,733 --> 00:04:56,973
deserves to die.

57
00:05:02,053 --> 00:05:02,572
Wenyu!

58
00:05:03,372 --> 00:05:04,012
Wenyu!

59
00:05:04,932 --> 00:05:05,653
Wenyu!

60
00:05:05,692 --> 00:05:06,572
Hold her down.

61
00:05:07,190 --> 00:05:09,590
Let her watch with her own eyes
as that wretched son of hers

62
00:05:09,853 --> 00:05:11,093
turns to ash!

63
00:05:11,093 --> 00:05:12,053
Wenyu!

64
00:05:12,692 --> 00:05:13,892
Wenyu!

65
00:05:14,012 --> 00:05:15,413
Wenyu…

66
00:05:15,772 --> 00:05:17,332
No…

67
00:05:17,932 --> 00:05:20,132
Wenyu!

68
00:05:52,853 --> 00:05:54,293
Liu Qinghe!

69
00:05:54,452 --> 00:05:54,932
Watch out!

70
00:05:55,012 --> 00:05:55,653
Mengyan!

71
00:06:02,692 --> 00:06:03,853
You will pay

72
00:06:04,372 --> 00:06:05,413
for your mistakes.

73
00:06:07,812 --> 00:06:08,372
Mengyan.

74
00:06:16,372 --> 00:06:17,892
Liu Qinghe…

75
00:06:19,053 --> 00:06:21,452
Let's see how long you survive.

76
00:06:21,613 --> 00:06:24,332
We'll meet again in the underworld.

77
00:06:41,772 --> 00:06:43,213
They say calamities live long.

78
00:06:43,220 --> 00:06:45,510
Her lower body was beaten to a pulp,
yet she still lived.

79
00:06:45,850 --> 00:06:47,690
Only because Young Madam Liu
has a kind heart.

80
00:06:48,332 --> 00:06:49,613
She's only alive

81
00:06:49,850 --> 00:06:51,590
becauseYoung Madam Liu
pleaded for her sake.

82
00:07:08,413 --> 00:07:09,093
You're awake.

83
00:07:20,812 --> 00:07:21,812
Shen…

84
00:07:22,973 --> 00:07:23,733
Wan…

85
00:07:24,812 --> 00:07:25,772
Wanqing…

86
00:07:26,973 --> 00:07:28,653
Why did you save me?

87
00:07:29,613 --> 00:07:30,572
What

88
00:07:31,493 --> 00:07:33,252
do you want?

89
00:07:33,772 --> 00:07:34,692
What do I want?

90
00:07:38,012 --> 00:07:39,213
I didn't save you

91
00:07:40,413 --> 00:07:41,572
out of pity.

92
00:07:43,493 --> 00:07:45,413
I want you to see

93
00:07:46,293 --> 00:07:47,132
for yourself

94
00:07:48,572 --> 00:07:50,332
how the Liu family

95
00:07:50,892 --> 00:07:53,252
and the power behind it
crumble step by step.

96
00:07:54,053 --> 00:07:54,613
You

97
00:07:56,572 --> 00:07:59,853
might as well have killed me.

98
00:08:06,413 --> 00:08:07,252
Death

99
00:08:09,493 --> 00:08:10,973
would be too easy.

100
00:08:27,093 --> 00:08:28,053
I want you

101
00:08:28,772 --> 00:08:30,973
to witness how the rules

102
00:08:32,052 --> 00:08:35,292
you relied on for survival

103
00:08:36,493 --> 00:08:39,892
get crushed beyond recognition.

104
00:08:42,973 --> 00:08:43,652
Only then

105
00:08:44,213 --> 00:08:46,213
will it match the sins you've committed.

106
00:09:09,093 --> 00:09:12,292
It's all karma…

107
00:09:13,093 --> 00:09:16,292
Retribution…

108
00:09:22,837 --> 00:09:23,786
(Memorial tablets
of the Seven Martyr Heroines)

109
00:09:23,810 --> 00:09:24,875
(Li Shushen, Liu Mingzhen,
and Shen Wanqing)

110
00:09:25,037 --> 00:09:27,980
(Memorial tablets of Liu clan ancestors
Liu Chengsi and Liu Huaiyuan)

111
00:09:28,093 --> 00:09:30,532
Xie Ruilan has received
the punishment she deserves.

112
00:09:31,012 --> 00:09:31,734
(Memorial tablets of Liu clan ancestors)
Liu Qinghe

113
00:09:31,758 --> 00:09:32,613
(Liu Chengsi and Liu Huaiyuan)
is next.

114
00:09:33,292 --> 00:09:35,172
Ancestors of the Liu clan,

115
00:09:35,453 --> 00:09:36,412
watch over me

116
00:09:36,933 --> 00:09:37,892
and guide me.
